      "message": "I still don\u0027t trust datastore secondary indexes, so i\u0027m wondering why previous ID scheme was not good enough?\n\n.Gte would work just fine and instead of Eq, you\u0027d need .Lte, but the upside is that primary index is used now, so you don\u0027t need secondary indexes. The downside is that VM.id scheme is now important.",
